d the ear of the horse:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) IKh explains it as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain bone behind the ear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"not particularizing a horse nor any other animal. (IB.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Msb","TA"]}]}}